			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><div class="postbody">ANNOUNCEMENT:  Veil of Shadows is Recruiting
<br />

<br />
Hello EverQuest Adventurers,
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="font-weight: bold">Guild Background</span></span>
<br />
Who are the Veil of Shadows?  We are a raiding guild that has been on Luclin for over two years.  We routinely raid the top encounters of the Luclin expansion.  In Plane of Power expansion, we have progressed to the pre-Elemental Plane stage of the game – all in-house.
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="font-weight: bold">Activity</span></span>
<br />
We attempt to balance the competitive environment within EverQuest and the real life needs we all have.  We know that most people cannot raid 7 nights per week for 6 hours at a time.  After all, EverQuest is a hobby and should not be a second job.  Our members understand that it takes a solid four nights per week to progress in our competitive server environment.
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="font-weight: bold">Recruitment</span></span>
<br />
As with many Planes of Power oriented guilds, the Veil of Shadows has to make adjustments in its recruitment policies.  <span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="font-style: italic">Enchanters, Magicians, Shaman, Beastlords, and Warriors</span></span>, that can raid 4 nights per week, are strongly encouraged to apply.  In addition to these classes, all others are encouraged to apply.  Here is an overview of our new recruitment policies: <ul>•  Our level requirements have been lowered for key classes.
<br />
•  We will have 2 rounds of back-flagging.  Additionally, we have formed  back-flagging agreements with several guilds.
<br />
•  For qualified applicants, we will assist with the completion of your Vex Thal key.  This zone offers some of the best loot in the game outside the Plane of Time.</ul> Contact <span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="font-style: italic">Nexium</span></span> in-game for recruitment inquiries or email him at <a href="mailto:msgnexium247@hotmail.com">msgnexium247@hotmail.com</a>.
<br />

<br />
Keep EverQuest Fun,
<br />
<a href="http://www.vosguild.org" target="_blank" class="postlink">Veil of Shadows</a><span class="gensmall"></span>


				</div></td>
